data.description: Fall color, cozy raised Ranch. 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms. Wonderful kitchen walks out onto beautiful back yard deck. Living room flows into formal dinning room. Master bedroom suite with his and her closets. Basement family room and pool table! Above ground swimming pool stays and the extra large fenced in back yard give so many outdoor living opportunities. Widowed owner downsizing to smaller home closer to grandchildren. Very emotional sell, not wanting to leave but wants to be closer to grandkids.
